summary: This FBI document details the arrest and transport of an individual on December 8, 2009, pursuant to a federal warrant for Obstruction of Justice issued by Magistrate Judge Linnea R. Johnson. The arrest occurred in or near West Palm Beach, Florida, and the individual was taken to the Palm Beach County Jail.

persons.name: Linnea R. Johnson
persons.context: Issued the arrest warrant for Obstruction of Justice on December 8, 2009.

events.title: Arrest for Obstruction of Justice
events.description: Agents made contact with and arrested an individual pursuant to a federal warrant issued by Magistrate Judge Linnea R. Johnson. The arrest occurred without incident, and the individual was transported to the Palm Beach County Jail.

keyFacts: An arrest warrant for Obstruction of Justice (18 U.S.C. ยง 1512(c)) was issued by U.S. Magistrate Judge Linnea R. Johnson on December 8, 2009.
The arrest was executed by federal agents in or near West Palm Beach, Florida, and was conducted without incident.
The arrested individual was transported to the Palm Beach County Jail.
The document is an FBI record (likely a 302 form) dated December 7, 2009, detailing an arrest that occurred on December 8, 2009.
